Package: ProfoundData
Title: A Package for downloading and exploring data from the PROFOUND database
Version: 0.2.1
Date: 2020-03-13
Authors@R: c(person("Ramiro", "Silveyra Gonzalez",  email = "rasilgon@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
